Class PrintStock

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.pane.resources.printall.stock.PrintStock
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class PrintStock
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    This class is a Controller loaded from a .fxml file.

    Presents the TableView of all the Orders and Transactions that were made with a specific Stock
